msgstr "Intel Core i5-9400F"

#: ../../02_getting-started/01_setup.md
msgid "Intel Core i7-13700K"
msgstr "Intel Core i7-13700K"

#: ../../02_getting-started/01_setup.md
msgid "GPU"
msgstr "GPU"

#: ../../02_getting-started/01_setup.md
